title: Ghost Emperor
summary: Ghost Emperor Manhua The comic tells the story of an atheistic teenager Jiang Chengfeng who, by accident, acquired a magical power. With this power, he can easily resolve the most terrifying and fearful events in the world. This time, the mission is to rescue a missing boy, and the location is the horrifying Kun Kunyan! See how he passes through all the way! Fighting evil spirits! Don’t pretend to be a ghost! Otherwise, they will all burst! The Advanced Soul 高等灵魂
